{"tid":1385421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegram 會自動show你電話號碼架！","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T09:53:34.000Z","uid":156623,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16caf8ce6b8bd78d46790e0afe60755492349bc0","tid":1385421,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"最近有人教Telegram 不同步個聯絡人名單<br />\n<br />\n咁不同步左後 咁你成個contact list自然冇曬人 點都要手動加返幾個兄弟姊妹親戚朋友<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但問題就黎啦</span><br />\n<br />\n手動加完個個聯絡人後 Telegram 係會自動幫你add個個聯絡人係 Always share with 到 <br />\n你個privacy 就會見到 No body(+1) 然後對方就會睇到你電話！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S6fi8xe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS6fi8xe.png&h=90770cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K803Acf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK803Acf.png&h=dc6b2d42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家識左新朋友 add左佢contact 記得去del返個 always share with !<br />\n<br />\n我同朋友仔試左一次 希望大家留意下"},{"pid":"c50554428b476957a25133440dbeccd8196655b3","tid":1385421,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f10afda3f6d0846e550abb2ce41d4fbfd96f9e","tid":1385421,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:33:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"bbe624a21740b827e37c0902d82cf90d3bee15c8","tid":1385421,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cda03c1bbc9a1d5c3272b76a6dbcae15d63d323","tid":1385421,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"係咪開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fca6004faa1f5ba7b43713871d3dbe46b77432","tid":1